=Are You The One=

13
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,980
=Episode 5=

14
00:01:43,980 --> 00:01:46,450
(Clear Winds and Auspicious Aura)

15
00:01:46,450 --> 00:01:47,290
My Lord!

16
00:01:49,610 --> 00:01:50,860
My Lord, where are you going?

17
00:01:51,100 --> 00:01:55,700
(Carrying Sunshine
and Accumulating Blessings)

18
00:02:02,100 --> 00:02:05,020
(Cui Mansion)

19
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:15,560
Jiu.

20
00:02:19,330 --> 00:02:20,170
Mrs. Cui.

21
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:09,870
You're so drunk.

22
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,260
Here, have some water.

23
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,240
Leave me alone.

24
00:03:22,650 --> 00:03:23,590
Let me help you change.

25
00:03:24,250 --> 00:03:25,220
Don't touch me.

26
00:03:33,770 --> 00:03:35,070
I know you're not feeling well.

27
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,840
The wine in the jar

28
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,980
smells sweet.

29
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,820
But it's in your stomach,

30
00:03:40,050 --> 00:03:41,330
in four or six hours,

31
00:03:41,330 --> 00:03:42,660
it will smell terrible.

32
00:03:43,530 --> 00:03:44,910
The bed linens

33
00:03:45,330 --> 00:03:46,280
are new

34
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,260
and still damp.

35
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,910
You'll get them smelly.

36
00:03:51,090 --> 00:03:52,260
Get out.

37
00:03:59,810 --> 00:04:01,750
Who knows what's in the wine they're selling?

38
00:04:02,250 --> 00:04:03,630
It's strong and harmful.

39
00:04:04,810 --> 00:04:06,350
Next time, if you want to drink,

40
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,650
I'll have Nanny Li

41
00:04:08,650 --> 00:04:10,310
get some fresh Xinfeng wine

42
00:04:10,650 --> 00:04:11,780
and warm it up for you.

43
00:04:13,770 --> 00:04:15,630
A warm drink

44
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:17,550
and a comfortable bed

45
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,260
is better than wandering the streets

46
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,500
and braving the cold.

47
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,630
Why don't you ask me

48
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,940
why I drank?

49
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,700
People say

50
00:04:31,210 --> 00:04:32,630
getting drunk eases sorrow.

51
00:04:33,210 --> 00:04:35,340
Who doesn't have tough times?

52
00:04:36,570 --> 00:04:38,340
Even the emperor

53
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,430
isn't always happy.

54
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:45,670
Though our house isn't
as grand as in the capital,

55
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,940
we're doing fine,
with everything we need covered.

56
00:04:48,770 --> 00:04:49,700
I've thought about it.

57
00:04:50,330 --> 00:04:52,110
Once the shop is running well

58
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:54,790
and covering our expenses,

59
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:57,490
maybe we can enjoy meat sometimes.

60
00:04:58,090 --> 00:04:59,340
Then, Jiu,

61
00:04:59,650 --> 00:05:01,040
you can go out,

62
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:01,990
play Go and visit friends.

63
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,550
Why does every worry

64
00:05:16,130 --> 00:05:18,430
in the world

65
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,500
seem trivial to you?

66
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,790
Since we are married,

67
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,790
we've never been afraid of

68
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:31,190
troubling each other.

69
00:05:32,970 --> 00:05:33,810
Jiu,

70
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,750
don't act tough with me.

71
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,430
If you ever feel tired,

72
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,430
just let go and rest.

73
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:43,870
I'll take care of everything.

74
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,870
Why are you looking at me?

75
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,940
I was just thinking.

76
00:06:11,650 --> 00:06:12,990
In this world,

77
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:16,900
no one ever told me

78
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,940
I could

79
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,560
have a rest

80
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,700
when I'm tired,

81
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:26,790
except you.

82
00:06:30,130 --> 00:06:31,500
Being born and living

83
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,990
in an ordinary family has its advantages.

84
00:06:36,690 --> 00:06:37,690
Alright,

85
00:06:37,690 --> 00:06:39,500
stop with the drunk talk.

86
00:06:39,890 --> 00:06:41,070
Let me help you

87
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:44,230
get comfortable and rest, okay?

88
