456
00:24:19,220 --> 00:24:20,060
If we could

457
00:24:20,500 --> 00:24:22,070
gain your support,

458
00:24:23,170 --> 00:24:25,510
the trade guild would certainly unite

459
00:24:26,120 --> 00:24:27,820
to support the court

460
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:30,580
