00:26:33,850 --> 00:26:35,230
Yes, we should meet them.

527
00:26:35,890 --> 00:26:36,850
Yes, we should.

528
00:26:36,850 --> 00:26:37,690
Exactly.

529
00:26:51,220 --> 00:26:52,140
A woman?

