he seems pretty straightforward.

875
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:47,150
When I asked him for a reward,
he just gave it to me.

876
00:41:49,370 --> 00:41:50,210
Miantang,

877
00:41:50,520 --> 00:41:52,100
you went to such lengths

878
00:41:53,410 --> 00:41:55,030
just to join the trade guild?

879
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:57,070
You know what.

880
00:41:57,410 --> 00:41:58,370
A large trade guild

881
00:41:58,370 --> 00:41:59,290
can be quite capricious.

882
00:41:59,290 --> 00:42:00,130
Alright, alright.

883
00:42:01,040 --> 00:42:01,880
I understand.

884
00:42:02,930 --> 00:42:04,120
You didn't take any

885
00:42:04,120 --> 00:42:06,030
of my words to heart.

886
00:42:09,810 --> 00:42:10,650
Miantang,

887
00:42:12,520 --> 00:42:14,350
staying in this house

888
00:42:14,600 --> 00:42:16,520
should be good enough,

889
00:42:16,520 --> 00:42:17,830
shouldn't it?

890
00:42:18,480 --> 00:42:19,970
Don't think about

891
00:42:19,970 --> 00:42:21,080
doing business

892
00:42:21,080 --> 00:42:22,740
or even joining the trade guild,

893
00:42:23,410 --> 00:42:24,250
okay?

894
00:42:24,330 --> 00:42:25,170
Why?

895
00:42:26,410 --> 00:42:27,330
You supported me

896
00:42:27,330 --> 00:42:28,370
in business before.

897
00:42:28,370 --> 00:42:29,370
Why does the trade guild

898
00:42:29,370 --> 00:42:31,180
seem to hit a nerve with you?

899
00:42:31,850 --> 00:42:33,700
Cui Jiu, what are you afraid of?

900
00:42:35,770 --> 00:42:36,610
I...

901
00:42:37,970 --> 00:42:40,910
Or were your encouraging words
just to placate me?

902
00:42:41,680 --> 00:42:42,870
Now that I often go out for work,

903
00:42:43,680 --> 00:42:44,910
does it make you uncomfortable?

904
00:42:47,390 --> 00:42:48,250
If that's what you think,

905
00:42:48,250 --> 00:42:49,510
I have nothing to say.

906
00:42:50,370 --> 00:42:51,260
Cui Jiu,

907
00:42:52,040 --> 00:42:54,120
I've never blamed you for being lazy.

908
00:42:54,120 --> 00:42:55,290
I willingly stand in front

909
00:42:55,290 --> 00:42:56,220
to shield you.

910
00:42:57,330 --> 00:42:59,260
But I don't want to see you so cowardly.

911
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:01,080
You want to achieve something

912
00:43:01,080 --> 00:43:02,390
but fear the trade guild,

913
00:43:02,930 --> 00:43:05,100
so you just hide in your shell.

914
00:43:05,600 --> 00:43:06,450
Likewise,

915
00:43:06,450 --> 00:43:07,410
you sweet-talk me without

916
00:43:07,410 --> 00:43:08,300
putting in the hard work,

917
00:43:08,430 --> 00:43:09,290
and at critical moments,

918
00:43:09,290 --> 00:43:11,070
you don't want me to make a public appearance.

919
00:43:11,560 --> 00:43:13,040
My husband can't be like that.

920
00:43:13,040 --> 00:43:13,880
I can be,

921
00:43:14,850 --> 00:43:15,690
but that's okay.

922
00:43:53,741 --> 00:43:59,971
♪The boat drifts,
bringing back the sunset♪

923
00:44:00,971 --> 00:44:07,091
♪When we reunite, we still joke
about the cause and effect♪

924
00:44:08,081 --> 00:44:14,331
♪Who passed by, the crabapple
falls with a turn♪

925
00:44:15,461 --> 00:44:18,701
♪Loving rightly but choosing wrong♪

926
00:44:19,041 --> 00:44:23,621
♪With joys, sorrows, partings and reunions♪

927
00:44:24,221 --> 00:44:30,881
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

928
00:44:31,631 --> 00:44:35,001
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

929
00:44:35,291 --> 00:44:38,621
♪Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

930
00:44:38,801 --> 00:44:45,571
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

931
00:44:45,951 --> 00:44:52,721
♪Long hidden in the eyes,
flickering in and out♪

932
00:44:53,221 --> 00:44:59,631
♪Let go of the flowers blooming
in the yard last night♪

933
00:45:00,471 --> 00:45:06,881
♪Let go of the waves in the stream
in half a lifetime♪

934
00:45:07,461 --> 00:45:14,081
♪Let those dust and chaos go on endlessly♪

935
00:45:14,881 --> 00:45:18,301
♪In this lifetime, my wish is to the vast sky♪

936
00:45:18,301 --> 00:45:23,401
♪There are many more♪

